Package image_filter

Class Summary
AveragingFilter applies an averaging filter to the given image.
ImageFilter ImageFilter is an abstract Class to implement a linear or nonlinear filter.
LaplacianFilter applies a laplacian filter to an image.
LinearImageFilter The linear imagefilter has coefficients. the size of the coefficient image is the width of the filter.
MedianFilter applies a median filter to the given image.
SobelOperator applies the sobel operator to an image.
 

Enum Summary
BorderHandling lists the methods for handling the borders of the images, when filters are applied.
